. do test_while.do 

. * while.do - Infinite while loop for SIGINT testing
. clear all

. set obs 1000
Number of observations (_N) was 0, now 1,000.

. gen x = runiform()

. gen y = x + rnormal()

. 
. di "Entering infinite loop at $S_DATE $S_TIME"
Entering infinite loop at 12 May 2026 15:25:39

. local i = 1

. while 1 {
  2.     quietly reg y x
  3.     quietly reg y x c.x##c.x
  4.     local i = `i' + 1
